<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Karamur Kartel</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-05-23 11:03:16</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>This belt is droped in Mines of Nurga. My group and I were the first to find this along with the Burynai Legion Gi which also is droped by the same thing.<BR>
<BR>
The items are droped from Burynai Slaves. Not Iksar slaves so dont try, Tho they might drop something. we killed so many we found nothing. Exploring the zone we found nothing but Goblins or spiders. Other than slaves its really not the type of zone for items. The Goblins dont have weapons (atleast we did not find any in the 4 hours we were there)<BR>
<BR>
The belt and Gi is droped every time. its either one of the other. They are lore so cant have any more then one. My suggestion is picking them up, casting on droped members to waist charges. then destroy them if your camping them. good way to get exp.<BR>
<BR>
-Karamur Kartel<BR>
31st season Vallon Zek server.<BR>
The First Dwarven Brigade<BR>
</font></td></tr></table>
